EXTRACTED VALUE: Both “x-treme” racing fans and racing aficionados alike will find something to enjoy, making it the possible Great Uniter of racing videogames.
All you developers out there who are just going to port over your games on the 360, take a note form Criterion. This how it’s supposed to be done.
If you are a fan of the genre and have been hoping for something new and fresh, this will suit you quite nicely.
While this game is pretty shallow in terms of content, it still becomes a great pickup for some mindless fun and destruction.
Fight Night is a fantastic game that even after the short career mode, will keep you going with it’s hard hitting and intense multiplayer.
